isSequenceEditsEnabled

public boolean isSequenceEditsEnabled()
Whether sequence edits are enabled. If sequenceEditsEnabled=false then getSequence() returns the concatenated exon sequence. If sequenceEditsEnabled=true and sequence edits exit for this transcritp then getSequence() returns the concatenated exon sequence with the edits applied.

Returns:
whether sequence edits are enabled. True by default.
See Also:
getSequence(), getSequenceEdits()
